AUDIO: 'pressure, and flow in the space around them. Because AR doesn\'t just make old software more convenient, it makes new experiences possible. Experiences that are useful,'

[07:31] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'shared, playful, and full of wonder. And with all of this capability, battery life is really important. So, we designed Specs for a range of'

[07:44] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'ways you might use them throughout your day. Specs offer up to 4 hours of mixed-use battery life, including audio and video playback, &gt;&gt; [applause] &gt;&gt; AI assistance, lenses, Bluetooth'

[08:02] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'notifications, and more. And the custom charging cable snaps into place magnetically. So, you can easily power Specs while'

