[08:40] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'immersive display. &gt;&gt; [cheering] [applause] &gt;&gt; And the included charging case offers four charges on the go, giving you up to 20 total hours'

[08:53] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'of mixed use. &gt;&gt; [applause] &gt;&gt; So, put simply, Specs are the most'

[09:05] [scene:talk]
